These are Puzzles for 2x5 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-8-1::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, swisher, siglo, dunhill, montecristo
The people use 5 different means of transport: boat, motorbike, ship, snowmobile, van
 1. the montecristo-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person driving the ship##5
 2. the ritmeester-smoker is the person driving the motorbike##1
 3. the person driving the motorbike is the ritmeester-smoker##1
 4. the dunhill-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person driving the van##5
 5. the person driving the van is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
 6. the montecristo-smoker is not to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##8
 7. the person driving the snowmobile is somewhere to the right of the person driving the boat##5
 8. the montecristo-smoker is not the person driving the ship##6
 9. the siglo-smoker is on the left or right of the swisher-smoker##3
10. the person driving the boat is not the dunhill-smoker##6
11. the person driving the motorbike is on the far right##1
12. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
13. the person driving the snowmobile is not to the left of the person driving the ship##8
14. the siglo-smoker is somewhere between the montecristo-smoker and the person driving the ship##7
15. the ritmeester-smoker is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |     2     |   3    |     4      |     5     |
| Cigar        | swisher | siglo | montecristo | dunhill     | ritmeester    |
| Transport   | ship | van       | boat   | snowmobile | motorbike |

