.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-8-2::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: blood-red, light-blue, turquise, lilac, red
There are 5 different nationalities: argentine, brazilian, british, malaysian, thai
 1. the person who likes red is somewhere to the left of the person who likes turquise##5
 2. the thai is not to the left of the argentine##8
 3. the person who likes light-blue is somewhere to the left of the british##5
 4. the argentine is somewhere to the left of the person who likes red##5
 5. the person who likes red is not to the right of the person who likes blood-red##8
 6. the brazilian is not the person who likes blood-red##6
 7. the argentine is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the malaysian is on the left of the thai##1
 9. the person who likes light-blue is somewhere to the right of the person who likes blood-red##5
10. the person who likes red is not to the right of the person who likes blood-red##8
11. the person who likes blood-red is the thai##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |     4     |    5    |
| Color   | lilac | red    | blood-red | light-blue  | turquise |
| Nationality   | argentine  | malaysian | thai      | brazilian | british |

