.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-8-3::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  architect, firefighter, mechanic, musician, police-officer
There are 5 different nationalities: dutch, spanish, british, canadian, indian
1. the architect is not to the right of the indian##8
2. the spanish is on the left or right of the british##3
3. the firefighter is between the canadian and the musician##2
4. the firefighter is the british##1
5. the police-officer is in the middle##1
6. the architect is on the left of the dutch##1
7. the architect is not to the left of the police-officer##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |       3        |     4     |     5     |
| Job           | musician | firefighter | police-officer | architect | mechanic  |
| Nationality   | spanish  | british        | canadian          | indian     | dutch |

