.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-8-4::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, water, sprite, tea, coffee
5 different pets are kept: cat, ferret, frog, goat, hamster
 1. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere between the person drinking water and the owner of the cat##7
 2. the owner of the frog is in an odd position##4
 3. the owner of the frog is somewhere to the right of the owner of the ferret##5
 4. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the right of the owner of the hamster##5
 5. the owner of the cat is on the far left##1
 6. the owner of the ferret is not the person drinking sprite##6
 7. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 8. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
 9. the owner of the ferret is somewhere between the person drinking sprite and the person drinking soy-milk##7
10. the owner of the ferret is not to the right of the person drinking water##8
11. the person drinking tea is the person drinking tea##1
12. the owner of the ferret is not the person drinking tea##6
13. the owner of the goat is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
14. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the right of the person drinking sprite##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4     |     5     |
| Beverage   | sprite | coffee | tea | soy-milk | water |
| Pet           | cat    | ferret | hamster    | goat      | frog      |

