 3. the person drinking water is between the malaysian and the brazilian##2
 4. the pakistani is the person drinking cola##1
 5. the nigerian is in an even position##4
 6. the person drinking mirinda is not to the left of the person drinking cola##8
 7. the nigerian is on the left or right of the malaysian##3
 8. the person drinking milk is between the person drinking cola and the person drinking water##2
 9. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the left of the nigerian##5
10. the person drinking fanta is the mexican##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2   |    3    |   4   |    5    |
