.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-8-6::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, iced-tea, lemonade, tea
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: sunflower, marigold, tulip, zinnia, amaryllis
 1. the person drinking lemonade is not to the left of the person who growsamaryllis##8
 2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
 3. the person who growssunflower is not to the left of the person drinking lemonade##8
 4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
 5. the person who growsmarigold is somewhere between the person who growsamaryllis and the person drinking almond-milk##7
 6. the person drinking tea is somewhere between the person drinking coffee and the person drinking lemonade##7
 7. the person who growsamaryllis is the person who growsamaryllis##1
 8. the person drinking lemonade is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person drinking tea##2
 9. the person who growstulip is not to the right of the person who growsamaryllis##8
10. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left or right of the person who growsmarigold##3
11. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
12. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |    2     |    3    |      4      |   5    |
| Beverage    | iced-tea | lemonade | tea     | almond-milk | coffee |
| Flower   | tulip    | amaryllis    | marigold | sunflower         | zinnia   |

