 5. the owner of the frog is somewhere to the left of the person drinking iced-tea##5
 6. the owner of the cat is not to the left of the person drinking lemonade##8
 7. the owner of the frog is not the person drinking iced-tea##6
 8. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the right of the person drinking lemonade##5
 9. the person drinking tea is not to the left of the person drinking lemonade##8
10. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
11. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
12. the owner of the ferret is somewhere to the left of the owner of the fish##5
13. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
