.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-8-8::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: drama, epic, fantasy, horror, western
The people have 5 different jobs:  designer, writer, social-worker, teacher, videographer
 1. the writer is not the person watching western movies##6
 2. the teacher is in the middle##1
 3. the person watching western movies is not to the left of the writer##8
 4. the writer is somewhere to the right of the person watching horror movies##5
 5. the person watching drama movies is not to the left of the social-worker##8
 6. the designer is somewhere to the left of the videographer##5
 7. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person watching horror movies is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the person watching drama movies is somewhere between the social-worker and the designer##7
10. the social-worker is in an odd position##4
11. the person watching drama movies is not the designer##6
12. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3    |  4   |    5    |
| Movie-Genre   | horror    | drama      | western | epic | fantasy |
| Job     | social-worker | writer | teacher    | designer  | videographer  |

