.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-8-9::.
House: palace, gothic-revival, futuristic, ranch-style, farmhouse
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: adventure, crime, disaster, family, romance
 1. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
 2. the person watching family movies is not to the left of the person watching romance movies##8
 3. the person watching family movies is on the left or right of the palace house##3
 4. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
 5. the person watching family movies is not to the left of the person watching romance movies##8
 6. the person watching romance movies is somewhere to the right of the farmhouse house##5
 7. the ranch-style house is somewhere to the right of the palace house##5
 8. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
 9. the palace house is on the left or right of the person watching crime movies##3
10. the ranch-style house is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3      |    4     |      5      |
| House           | farmhouse | palace | ranch-style | gothic-revival   | futuristic |
| Movie-Genre   | crime     | romance  | family     | disaster | adventure   |

