 4. the person who's sport is volleyball is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##5
 5. the person who's sport is parkour is somewhere to the right of the owner of the bird##5
 6. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person who's sport is skateboarding is in an odd position##4
 8. the owner of the snake is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is parkour##5
 9. the owner of the snake is not the person who's sport is soccer##6
10. the owner of the hedgehog is not to the left of the person who's sport is soccer##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |    4    |     5     |
