 7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is not to the right of the person drinking water##8
 8. the person drinking water is somewhere to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
 9. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
10. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere between the person drinking juice and the person who's sport is basketball##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |      3      |     4     |       5       |
